<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>For You, Dear Teacher</title>
    <!-- Elegant fonts & icons -->
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@400;700;900&family=Cormorant+Garamond:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            min-height: 100vh;
            background: #fbe9e7;  /* soft rose background */
            background-image: radial-gradient(circle at 30% 30%, rgba(255, 220, 220, 0.3) 0%, transparent 30%),
                              radial-gradient(circle at 80% 70%, rgba(255, 200, 210, 0.2) 0%, transparent 40%);
            font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 20px;
            position: relative;
        }

        /* handmade paper texture overlay */
        body::before {
            content: "";
            position: fixed;
            top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;
            background-image: url('data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="100" height="100" viewBox="0 0 100 100"><filter id="noise"><feTurbulence type="fractalNoise" baseFrequency="0.8" numOctaves="1" stitchTiles="stitch"/></filter><rect width="100" height="100" filter="url(%23noise)" opacity="0.05"/></svg>');
            pointer-events: none;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .card {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 10;
            max-width: 750px;
            width: 100%;
            background: rgba(255, 250, 245, 0.85);
            backdrop-filter: blur(3px);
            border-radius: 40px 12px 40px 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 30px 50px rgba(140, 80, 90, 0.25), 0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            padding: 50px 45px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 220, 220, 0.6);
            transition: all 0.4s ease;
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
        }

        .card:hover {
            box-shadow: 0 40px 70px rgba(160, 100, 120, 0.3);
            transform: translateY(-6px);
        }

        /* decorative corner florals */
        .corner {
            position: absolute;
            font-size: 3rem;
            color: #d49b9b;
            opacity: 0.4;
            z-index: 0;
        }
        .corner-tl {
            top: 15px; left: 20px;
            transform: rotate(-15deg);
        }
        .corner-br {
            bottom: 15px; right: 20px;
            transform: rotate(165deg);
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 4rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            color: #ac3f6b;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 0 0 10px;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            text-shadow: 3px 3px 0 #ffdbdb;
            line-height: 1.1;
            position: relative;
            display: inline-block;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            white-space: nowrap;
            border-bottom: 3px double #e8b6b6;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .greeting {
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #734b3a;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 30px 0 20px;
            font-style: italic;
        }

        .message {
            font-size: 1.7rem;
            line-height: 1.7;
            color: #3f2c1e;
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 550px;
            margin: 0 auto 30px;
            font-weight: 400;
            position: relative;
            padding: 0 15px;
        }

        .message i {
            color: #b9597a;
            font-size: 1.9rem;
        }

        .quote {
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #9d5784;
            margin: 30px 0 15px;
            text-align: center;
            border-left: 4px solid #e3a1a1;
            border-right: 4px solid #e3a1a1;
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 0 30px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, #fff2f0, transparent);
        }

        .flowers {
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 25px 0 20px;
            animation: sway 5s infinite ease-in-out;
        }

        @keyframes sway {
            0% { transform: rotate(0deg); }
            25% { transform: rotate(2deg); }
            75% { transform: rotate(-2deg); }
            100% { transform: rotate(0deg); }
        }

        .signature {
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #965252;
            text-align: right;
            margin-top: 45px;
            border-top: 2px dashed #eac0c0;
            padding-top: 25px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: flex-end;
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .signature i {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: #cf799b;
        }

        .stamp {
            background: #ffefef;
            border-radius: 50%;
            width: 70px;
            height: 70px;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            border: 2px solid #c28181;
            color: #a1495c;
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            transform: rotate(-10deg);
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px #ffe6e6;
        }

        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .card { padding: 30px 20px; }
            h1 { font-size: 3rem; white-space: normal; }
            .greeting { font-size: 1.8rem; }
            .message { font-size: 1.4rem; }
            .quote { font-size: 1.6rem; }
            .signature { font-size: 1.8rem; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="card">
        <!-- decorative corners -->
        <div class="corner corner-tl">🌹🌿</div>
        <div class="corner corner-br">🌿🌹</div>

        <h1>Happy Women's Day</h1>

        <div class="flowers">🌷🌸🌹🌼🌷</div>

        <div class="greeting">
            Dear <strong>Ofeliya Konstantinovna</strong>,
        </div>

        <div class="message">
            <i class="fas fa-feather-alt" style="margin-right: 10px;"></i>
            On this beautiful spring day, I want to thank you for the light of knowledge you bring into our lives.  
            Your lessons are like poetry, and your kindness — like the first warm rays of March sun.  
            <i class="fas fa-feather-alt" style="margin-left: 10px;"></i>
        </div>

        <div class="quote">
            “She turned the pages of our hearts<br>with the gentleness of spring.”
        </div>

        <div class="message">
            May your day be filled with blossoms, joy, and the sweetest surprises.  
            You deserve all the beauty this world can offer.
        </div>

        <div class="signature">
            <span class="stamp">❤️</span>
            <span>With deepest respect and love,<br><strong>Kirill</strong></span>
            <i class="fas fa-heart"></i>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
